{"tid":2034693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅提「一中原則」，台外交部：國際上只有台灣民選政府有權代表台灣人，中國無權說三道四","createTime":"2020-05-25T11:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T15:38:45.000Z","uid":1886,"like":157,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf9e51fd0a5e1bd04e9ccea4f1d0c3465c6205d","tid":2034693,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:30:37.000Z","msg":"中國外交部長王毅昨日再次提「一中原則」。台灣外交部昨晚指出，台灣已是公認民主國家，前途只有台灣人民有權決定，國際上也只有台灣民選政府有權代表台灣人民，中國無權說三道四。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200525/WLFE3W5B6ANQNJW7IBXBHFNZDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200525%2FWLFE3W5B6ANQNJW7IBXBHFNZDE%2F&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3oRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=c27a90ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200525%2FWLFE3W5B6ANQNJW7IBXBHFNZDE%2F&h=a0e4aa91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200525/WLFE3W5B6ANQNJW7IBXBHFNZDE/</a>"},{"pid":"b4b50d638728e42d55cd95a9152105cc7e439146","tid":2034693,"uid":1886,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:31:10.000Z","msg":"台灣外交部又指，中共政府不問台灣人民意願而欲強加「統一」於民主台灣，只凸顯其蔑視民意，敵視民主，與民主國家共享價值毫不相容。此外，總統蔡英文5月20日宣誓就職演說強調，台灣將堅守「和平、對等、自由、民主」原則處理兩岸交流、促進海峽和平穩定。台灣拒絕北京當局矮化台灣、破壞現狀的「一國兩制」主張，兩岸穩定發展雙方都有責任，而大陸在國際上阻止其他國家與台灣往來，打壓台灣人民貢獻國際事務，與兩岸和平穩定發展背道而馳。"},{"pid":"4c6df0bd07db3d54f1583e1435d16659ccf9bf7d","tid":2034693,"uid":25105,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:33:53.000Z","msg":"Taiwan: just shut the fuck up"},{"pid":"dfc1ba13f03186a279a26f33d89d5229f4a861ed","tid":2034693,"uid":301952,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"指手劃腳 說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85f87ce6d9ae9fc4d12b11681c91245522197c8","tid":2034693,"uid":68463,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"支那死纏爛打 好肉酸<img src=\"/ass